comment._content: If you're interested in ancient history, a sketch of the Dubbo Court House appeared in an illustrated article on Dubbo which ran in the Sydney Mail, 24/11/1888. The following link gets you to the article...the pic of the courthouse appears on the front of the Illustrated Supplement (back a few pages) - news.google.com/newspapers?id=LP1UAAAAIBAJ&sjid=VZMDA...
